'''Kathryn Mullen''' is a puppeteer who assisted [[Frank Oz]] with the puppeteering of [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']].

Mullen began performing with the Muppets on ''[[The Muppet Show]]'' in 1978. She also went on to perform [[W:c:Muppet:Mokey Fraggle|Mokey]] on [[W:c:Muppet:Fraggle Rock|''Fraggle Rock'']].

She worked as a puppeteer on another [[Lucasfilm]] production, ''Labyrinth'', directed by Jim Henson.

